
        B a s i l i c P l u s   I n s t a l l a t i o n

Read install.html for configuration and installation instructions.

The installation loop goes like this :
- Edit "configure" to tune the configuration options.
- Run ./configure to apply these settings.
- Open checkConfig.php in a browser to check your configuration status.

Basilic has been tested with:
- mysql 5.1.54
- php 5.3.5
- apache 2.2.17-1
- htmldoc 1.8.27-4 ( not mandatory )

Import has been tested with:
- python 2.7.1
- python-bibtex 1.2.5

